# Shipped to the AUR repo by CI (release.yml `assets`). With assets present
# the deploy action stages `git add --all`, so without this file the source
# tarball downloaded by updpkgsums lands in the AUR commit — and aurweb
# rejects blobs larger than ~488 KiB (DEC-145).
*.tar.gz
*.tar.xz
*.tar.zst
src/
pkg/
